entry.value: Find directions on Google Maps or your location to USIU-Africa,Nairobi Kenya
Public transit does not go directly to USIU. Make sure you search the directions on Google Map properly
Complementary bike parking will be available at USIU. Security officers will provide secure valet parking for your bicycle from 8 am until the event ends
You can share rides with your colleagues to and from the event using either of the famous taxi hailing services

Parking is very limited and available only in USIU designated slots located in USIU-Africa. If you plan to drive,we recommend carpooling with other attendees as preferred parking spaces will be available for cars containing two or more people
